summary: I’m always eager to learn and improve, and I aim to understand what I’m doing as best as possible. My primary interest is FX, specifically with Houdini, because I love the procedural workflow and flexibility of the software. However, I have a variety of other skills, both creative and technical, and am happy to contribute to a team in any way I can to achieve the best result possible.
